# Tutorial
- *Theoretical preliminaries*
  - [Logic Program with Annotated Disjunctions (LPAD)](tutorial/lpad.swinb)
- *Basic examples with exact inference*
  - [Coin](tutorial/inference/coin.swinb). Simple unconditional inference.
  - [Dice](tutorial/inference/dice.swinb). Conditional inference and inference with graphical results.
  - [Epidemic](tutorial/inference/epidemic.swinb). LPAD with implicit _null_ atom in the clauses, noisy or between rule groundings.
  - [Earthquake](tutorial/inference/earthquake.swinb) noisy or between different rules.
  - [Medical symptoms](tutorial/inference/sneezing.swinb) noisy or between different rules.
